---
title: Damian Walsh
description: UX/UI designer based in London, UK with over 15 years experience in agency and client side roles for FTSE listed companies across financial, publishing and retail sectors.
header_image: header-image.jpg
---

<div class="site-main-section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="pad-one-col">
      <h2>About me</h2>
      <p class="lede">I design user-friendly interfaces informed by research and best practices which balance user needs with business objectives.</p>
    </header>
    <h3>Skills</h3>
    <div class="grid-layout-three-col">
      <div class="grid-layout-item">
        <svg width="68" height="68" viewBox="0 0 68 68" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" class="icon">
          <title>User Experience Design</title>
          <g transform="translate(1 1)" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
            <circle stroke="#333" cx="33" cy="33" r="33" class="icon-border"/>
            <g stroke="#333" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-graphic">
              <path d="M27.855 44.5H37.5V39c0-.63-3.847-2.74-7-4v-2.5s1.24-.42 1.24-3.13c.876 0 1.26-2.522.04-2.522 0-.267.965-1.65.59-3.152-.63-2.522-6.935-2.522-7.565 0-2.655-.543-.63 2.788-.63 3.152-1.26 0-.88 2.522-.002 2.522 0 2.71 1.328 3.13 1.328 3.13V35c-3.152 1.26-7 3.37-7 4v5.5h9.355z"/>
