            </g>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <h4>User Experience Design</h4>
        <p>Producing wireframes and interactive prototypes, conducting user research and testing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-layout-item">
        <svg width="68" height="68" viewBox="0 0 68 68" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" class="icon">
          <title>Visual Design</title>
          <g transform="translate(1 1)" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
            <circle stroke="#333" cx="33" cy="33" r="33" class="icon-border"/>
            <g stroke="#333" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-graphic">
              <path d="M39.5 33.5H41c2.09 0 3.5 1.5 3.5 3.5s-1.41 3.5-3.5 3.5h-1.5M39.5 45c0 1.47-1.107 2.5-2.5 2.5H26c-1.393 0-2.5-1.108-2.5-2.5V31.5h16V45zM39.807 18.58c1.3 1.985-.627 3.074-1.076 4.14-.474 1.127-.012 2.208 1.117 2.683 3.657 1.542 4.745-5.664-.04-6.822zM35.959 31.5l3.54-6.354M40.775 25.618l-2.23 5.882M28.5 31.5h-4l-2-4-.5-4 3.5 2 3 6zM22.5 27.5l3-2M35.5 18.5h-6v13h6v-13zM35.5 21.5h-3M35.5 23.5h-2M35.5 25.5h-3M35.5 28.5h-2"/>
            </g>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <h4>Visual Design</h4>
        <p>Establishing and working within existing guidelines to create consistent on-brand user interfaces.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-layout-item">
        <svg width="68" height="68" viewBox="0 0 68 68" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" class="icon">
          <title>Front-end Development</title>
          <g transform="translate(1 1)" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd">
            <circle stroke="#333" cx="33" cy="33" r="33" class="icon-border"/>
            <g stroke="#333" class="icon-graphic">
              <path d="M24.5 45.5h18M33 42.5v3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M18.5 37.5h29"/>
              <path d="M47.5 40.5c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2h-25c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2v-19c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h25c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v19z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
